            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nThis text is a continuation of the previous one (htcite0>); therefore, we recommend reading that first. In addition, we suggest studying *Natural Limits* (<htcite1>), as it presents a fundamental concept that we will explore here.",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "efd81f99-fe84-43cc-81aa-5efe294b702c",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
